text: Keegan-Michael Key (born March 22, 1971) is an American actor and comedian. Key was born in Southfield, Michigan. He and Jordan Peele have a comedy show on MADtv. == References == Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Michigan Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from Michigan
